<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ910510-0176</DOCNO><DOCID>910510-0176.</DOCID><HL>   Charming Shoppes Sales Climb</HL><DATE>05/10/91</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A5C</SO><CO>   CHRS</CO><MS>CONSUMER CYCLICAL (CYC)</MS><IN>ALL SPECIALTY RETAILERS (RTS)SPECIALTY APPAREL RETAILERS (SAP)</IN><RE>PENNSYLVANIA (PA)</RE><LP>   BENSALEM, Pa. -- Charming Shoppes Inc. said sales in thefour weeks ended last Saturday rose 10%, to $73.9 million,and climbed 3% on a comparable-store basis.   It said sales in the three months ended Saturday rose 16%,to $222.9 million, while year-to-date comparable-store salesincreased 8%.</LP><TEXT>   The company operates 1,057 stores in 41 states, primarilyunder the names &quot;Fashion Bug&quot; and &quot;Fashion Bug Plus.&quot;</TEXT></DOC>